 wird Kants Text in diesem Band "entschlüsselt": interpretiert, auf seine systematische Überzeugungskraft und auf seine politische Tragweite hin untersucht und in seinen und unseren sozialgeschichtlichen Kontext gestellt.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aFrieden. 4aImmanuel Kant. 4aPhilosophie. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aBrandt, Reinhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCastillo, Monique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDoyle, Michael W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGerhardt, Volker, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHöffe, Otfried, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHöffe, Otfried, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKersting, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaberge, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMerle, Jean-Christophe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSaner, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 1990 - 1999z9783110636901oZDB-23-GPH0 cprintz978305002693040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978305007081040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050070810423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050070810/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GPHc1990d1999